title: The Bootleg Project-BFW,K.Raydio,Mike Dreams,Shad,William S. Bur
description:
The Bootleg Project:

Over the years I have collected about 6,000 live shows, studio outtake compilations and other various bootlegs. I have decided to share these with everyone. I am starting with artists who have the fewest shows and working my way up. I am doing it this way to be able to put out a lot of shows fast and work my way up to artists who have hundreds of shows. Feel free to share these with anyone you want. My goal is to hopefully expose people to music they have never heard before and create some new fans for musicians who deserve more recognition. My other goal is to spread rare stuff that deserves to see the light of day and be heard by as many people as possible. Enjoy!


NOTE: I will be sharing these for one month and will be deleting them from my seedbox in order to keep the shows coming. If everyone gives back what they take, these will stay alive forever, so please keep seeding once are done downloading and don't hit and run. Thanks!

Included in this torrent are bootlegs from:

Benjamin Francis Leftwich
K.Raydio
Mike Dreams
Shad
William S. Burroughs (w/ Kurt Cobain)
